1
00:00:00,140 --> 00:00:03,060
=The Crow Princess of Fortune=

2
00:00:03,060 --> 00:00:04,980
=Episode 25=

3
00:00:07,200 --> 00:00:10,080
Xiao Heng called me Mother
for twenty years.

4
00:00:10,400 --> 00:00:13,120
He was always respectful
and obedient to me.

5
00:00:13,480 --> 00:00:15,400
No matter how I beat
or scolded him before,

6
00:00:15,920 --> 00:00:18,080
he still longed for my love.

7
00:00:18,440 --> 00:00:19,640
Little did he know

8
00:00:19,640 --> 00:00:20,880
his real mother

9
00:00:21,280 --> 00:00:22,920
was killed by me.

10
00:00:22,920 --> 00:00:24,060
Hahaha!

11
00:00:24,060 --> 00:00:25,680
Hahaha!

12
00:00:35,320 --> 00:00:36,360
Xiao Heng!

13
00:00:41,640 --> 00:00:44,920
Hahaha!

14
00:00:44,920 --> 00:00:46,480
You came at the perfect time.

15
00:00:47,800 --> 00:00:49,720
My beloved pets

16
00:00:50,040 --> 00:00:52,200
have been hungry
for a long time already.

17
00:00:52,200 --> 00:00:54,080
Since you've
delivered yourself to my door,

18
00:00:54,080 --> 00:00:56,640
you'll make
the perfect extra meal for them.

19
00:00:57,920 --> 00:01:05,080
Hahaha!

20
00:01:05,240 --> 00:01:07,440
I've been setting up
this formation here for years.

21
00:01:07,440 --> 00:01:09,400
All that was missing

22
00:01:09,400 --> 00:01:10,960
was this final step.

23
00:01:11,240 --> 00:01:15,520
I needed the flesh and blood
of someone with dragon aura

24
00:01:15,520 --> 00:01:17,440
to serve as the core of the formation.

25
00:01:18,600 --> 00:01:20,320
I originally planned to capture you,

26
00:01:20,520 --> 00:01:23,040
but now you've
delivered yourself here instead.

27
00:01:23,440 --> 00:01:25,560
Hahaha!

28
00:01:27,600 --> 00:01:29,200
After today,

29
00:01:29,480 --> 00:01:31,840
the world will be turned upside down,

30
00:01:32,720 --> 00:01:35,200
and I will rule over everything.

31
00:01:35,440 --> 00:01:36,240
Go.

32
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:52,640
This...

33
00:01:54,800 --> 00:01:56,600
How is this possible?

34
00:01:57,800 --> 00:01:58,920
I've fed these snakes

35
00:01:59,520 --> 00:02:02,160
with my blood for years.

36
00:02:02,960 --> 00:02:04,480
How could they possibly obey you?

37
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:12,800
All beasts return to their master

38
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:13,960
and obey my command.

39
00:02:14,320 --> 00:02:17,360
With your crooked little tricks,
what right do you have to command them?

40
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:18,440
Get him!

41
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:19,600
Bite him!

42
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:21,080
How dare you!

43
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:23,480
Go!

44
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:28,160
Ah!

45
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:33,640
Hey.

46
00:02:33,640 --> 00:02:35,040
Don't just bite his legs.

47
00:02:35,040 --> 00:02:36,640
Take a few bites at his backside too.

48
00:02:36,640 --> 00:02:38,080
And don't forget the venom.

49
00:02:44,600 --> 00:02:45,560
Hm?

50
00:02:45,720 --> 00:02:47,560
Running pretty fast, aren't you?

51
00:02:54,680 --> 00:02:56,560
You... You stay away from me.

52
00:02:57,160 --> 00:02:58,600
I'm the Consort, you...

53
00:03:03,440 --> 00:03:05,280
Hahaha!

54
00:03:06,760 --> 00:03:08,240
Xiao Heng,

55
00:03:08,480 --> 00:03:11,160
I killed your real mother.

56
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:14,320
You called me Mother for twenty years.

57
00:03:14,320 --> 00:03:15,440
Isn't that pathetic?

58
00:03:17,520 --> 00:03:19,400
So what if I lost?

59
00:03:20,440 --> 00:03:24,640
No one in this life
will ever truly care about you!

60
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:31,760
Who told you

61
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:34,840
that no one cares about me?

62
00:03:35,480 --> 00:03:36,040
Exactly.

63
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:38,360
Where do you think that leaves me?

64
00:03:38,400 --> 00:03:40,040
Don't think I don't know.

65
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:42,600
You're only trying to anger my Father

66
00:03:42,600 --> 00:03:43,640
so you can die quickly.

67
00:03:43,640 --> 00:03:45,560
You never even paid me protection money,

68
00:03:46,080 --> 00:03:47,960
I won't let you get your way.

69
00:03:49,720 --> 00:03:51,760
Bad Consort, tell me,

70
00:03:52,200 --> 00:03:55,400
once your son is reduced to a commoner,

71
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:58,600
living in a leaking shack,

72
00:03:58,600 --> 00:04:01,560
eating spoiled leftovers every day,

73
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:04,920
with no one to turn to

74
00:04:04,920 --> 00:04:06,360
and no one coming to help

75
00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:09,680
do you think he'll hate you?

76
00:04:09,880 --> 00:04:12,000
Will he wish

77
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:15,000
he never had a mother like you?

78
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:16,960
You... You're a devil!

79
00:04:17,880 --> 00:04:19,040
A devil?

80
00:04:19,040 --> 00:04:20,880
I am a lucky star.

81
00:04:20,880 --> 00:04:24,440
But even lucky stars
believe in fairness.

82
00:04:24,640 --> 00:04:26,280
If evil people get happy endings,

83
00:04:26,280 --> 00:04:28,080
that would be truly unfair.

84
00:04:28,280 --> 00:04:29,280
That's right.

85
00:04:29,760 --> 00:04:31,720
I want you to stay alive.

86
00:04:32,560 --> 00:04:34,920
Stay alive and watch Xiao Jing
be stripped of his title.

87
00:04:35,280 --> 00:04:38,680
Watch all your glory
and riches disappear.

88
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:43,760
Watch all your schemes end in nothing.

89
00:04:45,160 --> 00:04:46,680
Father, let's go.

90
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:49,040
Let's go ask Grandfather for a reward.

91
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:54,880
You...

92
00:04:57,160 --> 00:05:00,600
Devil!

93
00:05:10,100 --> 00:05:13,300
♪Little lucky star,
twinkling with a wink at me♪

94
00:05:13,420 --> 00:05:16,980
♪Every Chinese New Year day brings
the luckiest fortune slip♪

95
00:05:17,260 --> 00:05:20,460
♪The God of Wealth favors me,
the Matchmaker ties red strings for me♪

96
00:05:20,780 --> 00:05:23,420
♪With firecrackers going off,
good things keep coming one after another♪

97
00:05:24,620 --> 00:05:27,980
♪Make a wish on the very first day
of the Chinese New Year♪

98
00:05:28,260 --> 00:05:31,700
♪By the second day,
my belly's already round♪

99
00:05:32,100 --> 00:05:35,420
♪Always talking about dieting,
but the chub never disappears♪

100
00:05:35,420 --> 00:05:39,140
♪Good food brings joy
and happiness every single day♪

101
00:05:45,060 --> 00:05:48,420
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
every year is filled with joy♪

102
00:05:48,740 --> 00:05:52,140
♪I'm bringing blessings to everyone♪

103
00:05:52,380 --> 00:05:55,780
♪Hands clasped together in greeting♪

104
00:05:56,100 --> 00:05:59,460
♪May every family be sweet and happy♪

105
00:05:59,740 --> 00:06:03,140
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
may everything go your way♪

106
00:06:03,420 --> 00:06:05,340
♪Endlessly flowing♪

107
00:06:05,340 --> 00:06:11,220
♪Good fortune♪
